{
  "texts": [
    "Running prompts on a fine-tuned chat-gpt-3.5-turbo incurs 6 times the cost per input token compared to the standard gpt-3.5-turbo as of February 2024.",
    "Note: gpt-3.5-fine-tune is a fine-tune on top of gpt-3.5-turbo-1106 using 300 sentences for fine-tuning.",
    "The remaining 700 sentences of the validation set are used for evaluating the models.",
    "The few shot prompt includes all 300 sentences and the assigned label in the conversion history of Gemini before classifying new excerpts.",
    "Architecturally similar to ChatGPT, Gemini are a family of decoder-only transformer models that are developed by Google."
  ]
}